                    <span>I could not put this book down once I started to read it. It captured my attention from the first page. It gives you such an insight on this woman's life and the different culture and ways that these men treat their women.<BR>It shows how strong the human spirit can be and how you can overcome adversity.<BR>You sometimes live in your own little world and don't realize what goes on in other countries. It sure does open up your eyes and your heart. A must read!!</span>
                  
